latestPosts.caption: Wrapped in slow moments and silver details 🤍

Sukoon- a feeling, a memory, a pause.
This collection is a tribute to the quiet joy found in slow, mindful creation. Each piece is handwoven and hand embroidered by skilled artisans who carry forward the legacy of Phulkari with patience and love. The intricate detailing you see is not just design- it’s hours of labour, emotion and soul stitched into fabric.

In a word that rushes, Sukoon invites you to slow down, to breathe, and to embrace timeless beauty that can’t be hurried.
.
.
📍Find us at: Lal Kothi, Opposite Power House,New Garden Enclave, South City 2, Ludhiana.
.
.
Muse:@harsohenajaggi
Photography: @akshaysammi @amishasammi 
Managed by: @ekahmedia 
.
